mayan_temple: Have you seen those large|statues at the entrance?
I didn't think it was true|but the gate really did open.
Did you hear that earthquake|and come running here as well?
default: I've found some RARE Dynamons!

I'm looking for ancient relics!

default: This is going to be easy!
Our boss say's I'm the strongest trainer.

I'm not from around here,|do you want to see my dynamons?

bossBattle.taunt: You're new here, right? Let's battle!
You've reached far enough!
How about a friendly match?
I may be OLD, but I can|still enjoy a good battle!
It's a beautiful day to FIGHT!
Isn't it an honor to battle?
Stay out of the way!
We are busy, stop disturbing us!
Stay away from the volcano!
Can't let you pass here!
You can't be here!
This is going to get hotter!
Leave NOW, or else...
Rumor has it, that you wanna battle?|Prove me right!
I heard from others that|Ramethyst could be found here
Look at this new Dynamon I caught!
Hey Champ, I'm gonna beat your team!
There may be lots of new Dynamons here,|but have you seen my Rexaroo!
You wanna know where Ramethyst is? Well, let's|see if you have what it takes to beat me first.
I know the secret location of Ramethyst|and I won't tell you unless you win.
Of course you'd be here. There's|nothing of interest here for you, go home.
I thought you wouldn't|see me behind this large statue.
Gah! I didn't see you coming, I'm not ready.

content.text: Welcome to COSTA GUESTA!
Did you come here to become|a Dynamon Captain?
Let's start by testing your SKILLS!
NICE! you have great potential.|Now choose your own Dynamon!
Great choice, you will make a great team!
Now, I have something to give you...
These ITEMS will be useful in your journey.
Speaking of which,|let's find a WILD DYNAMON...
Let's find some wild|Dynamons to BATTLE!
WAIT! Now that it's weak, let's|try to CATCH it!
WOW! Your Dynamon can LEVEL UP!
We use SHARDS to do that.|Use some now!
You can SWITCH Dynamons during battle.
Let's use the Duxedo you just caught!
That's Patrik, he also trains in the Camp...
Go and BATTLE him!
During battles, you can use one ITEM per turn.
Use the SKILL CAN you just got!
Dynamons and Skills have TYPES...
Use the STRONG type when possible!
You got access to a new location.
Let's go there!
Yo! Welcome to Costa Gueta,|my name is Dario...
The sea today is TOTALLY AWESOME, but|I'd rather practice my battle technique!
WOW, you're AWESOME!|I still have a lot to learn...
If you need anything - I'll hang here!
Behold the glory of the Mighty Shellby!
Thousand of years ago on this rock,|the Mighty Shellby gave birth to all we know!
We, the Brotherhood of Shells,|have sworn to protect this island FOREVER!
By the name of the Mighty Shellby,|you are NOT welcome here!
Prepare to fight the members|of the Brotherhood!
Are you still here?!
The Mighty Shellby will give our|Brotherhood the power to defeat you!
Your presence here is an INSULT|to the Mighty Shellby!
Oh, Mighty Shellby, give me the|strength to defeat this intruder!
HAHA! You are nothing compared with the|power of the glorious Shellbys!
You've won? This cannot be!
The Mighty Shellby works in mysterious ways...|Perhaps you were destined to win!
YES! That's right!|It is now our duty to grant you a reward...
Keep this gift as a token for the|strength the Mighty Shellby has given you!
Don't come any closer!
I have travelled here to seek a Dragon|and I will not be bothered by you!
My mercenaries will keep you out!
I've warned you no to come here...
Now you shall pay! Meet my KRIMSON!
My Krimson... has LOST?!
It is useless to me now...|If you want it, go ahead and CATCH it!
Oh my, that was a tough fight!|Fancy a rematch?
I see you haven't found it either.|I'll keep looking!
That was so cool,|isn't Pandinky so amazing!
Well Champ, you did good!
I'll be back!! Next time|with more Rexaroos!
Violet seems to be the one who|knows where it is, I'm sorry I don't know!
Oh wow, that was a tough fight.|Even Ramethyst couldn't beat you.
If you still want to know,|Ramethyst can be found|at the base of the waterfall.
Ahaha the secret stays with me,|better luck next time!
Guardians told me you might be close behind.
I'm sure you're also here seeking|information on the what caused it.
Wait... did you hear that? Yes I know you won,|but that loud quaking noise?
There was a loud quaking noise outside...|I have to go and check it out.|Take your prize and go.
I found gryphon in this room,|maybe you can too.
You think that'll stop me?
Try again next time,|if you think you're up to the challenge.
